{"id":10186,"date":"2024-01-08T19:20:25","date_gmt":"2020-06-08T13:50:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=10186"},"modified":"2024-10-26T19:36:40","modified_gmt":"2024-10-26T14:06:40","slug":"bathroom-mirror-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/bathroom-mirror-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Stunning Bathroom Mirror Design Ideas that will Make You Feel More Beautiful"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Because why should bathroom mirrors bore you to death?<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It would be an understatement to say that bathroom mirrors are the focal pieces that actually make or break your powder room. Mirrors not only tell you how you look, feel but also elevate the decor of your bathroom. When it comes to style, bathroom mirrors are absolutely irreplaceable.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also mounting a mirror of the right size for your bathroom not only makes it look more spacious but it allows it to seem more well-lit too. Quintessentially, it also ups the design game of your washroom and gives a nice character to the walls.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, get the most trendy bathroom mirrors for your home, rely on our cherry picked recommendations for bathroom mirror ideas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Fancy Corner Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Corners and wall merges are some of the most underutilized areas, especially in a bathroom.&nbsp; A curvy and neatly etched mirror like this can make the most of it for you. Also, it makes your bathroom look more stylish and owing to its smart design keeps getting attention as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184415\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-fancy-corner-mirror.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom mirror design with corner bathroom mirrors are perfect for creating a class bathroom\" class=\"wp-image-10190\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184415\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-fancy-corner-mirror.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184415\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-fancy-corner-mirror-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184415\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-fancy-corner-mirror-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184415\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-fancy-corner-mirror-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Curved, corner bathroom mirrors are perfect for creating a class apart washroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Wooden Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Though seemingly simple, wooden mirrors succeed at granting a stunning look to your bathroom. If you like bathroom mirrors that do not need much care but are great to stare as well then wooden mirrors should be on your mind.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08185513\/wooden-mirror-for-bathroom.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom mirrors with a wooden mirror for your bathroom to make simplicity and class bathroom\" class=\"wp-image-10195\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08185513\/wooden-mirror-for-bathroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08185513\/wooden-mirror-for-bathroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08185513\/wooden-mirror-for-bathroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08185513\/wooden-mirror-for-bathroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Choose a wooden mirror for your bathroom to exude simplicity and class<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Mirror, mirror on the wall, these designs outshine them all\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/26184543\/mirror-designs-outshine-them-all.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Vintage Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For that slice of nostalgia and in the name of the good old days, a vintage mirror will work really well for your bathroom. It\u2019s subtle detailing and textures can make you fall in love with yourself every time you look at it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08185836\/vintage-bathroom-mirrors.jpg\" alt=\"Vintage bathroom mirrors will make your bathroom richer\" class=\"wp-image-10198\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08185836\/vintage-bathroom-mirrors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08185836\/vintage-bathroom-mirrors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08185836\/vintage-bathroom-mirrors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08185836\/vintage-bathroom-mirrors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A vintage mirror will make your bathroom richer<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sideway Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Extremely functional and interesting to see, a sideway mirror plays a vital role in creating a trendy bathroom. Not too mention how chic and sleek it looks overall. This is one of those bathroom mirrors that goes absolutely well with a modern washroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190135\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-sideway-mirror.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom mirror design with a sideway mirror plays a vital role in creating a trendy bathroom\" class=\"wp-image-10201\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190135\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-sideway-mirror.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190135\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-sideway-mirror-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190135\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-sideway-mirror-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190135\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-sideway-mirror-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Want your bathroom to look chicer? Get a sideway mirror then<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Shapely Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Although edgier mirrors have a charm of their own, often an out of the box design like that of a shapely mirror can completely enhance your bathroom. With neat and rounded edges, the shapely mirror grants subtle style to your bathroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190311\/shapely-bathroom-mirrors.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom wall mirrors with shapely mirror to set the tone for a stylish bathroom\" class=\"wp-image-10202\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190311\/shapely-bathroom-mirrors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190311\/shapely-bathroom-mirrors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190311\/shapely-bathroom-mirrors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190311\/shapely-bathroom-mirrors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Set the tone for a stylish bathroom with a shapely mirror<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Statement Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who does not like a statement piece in a bathroom? A statement mirror carved in metal lets you do just that! You may choose brass or any other metal to design such a mirror. Either way, your bathroom will now transform into a royal chamber. Isn\u2019t that exciting?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184249\/bathrom-washroom-mirrors-with-statement-mirror.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom washroom mirrors with a statement mirror to create a regal bathroom\" class=\"wp-image-10189\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184249\/bathrom-washroom-mirrors-with-statement-mirror.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184249\/bathrom-washroom-mirrors-with-statement-mirror-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184249\/bathrom-washroom-mirrors-with-statement-mirror-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184249\/bathrom-washroom-mirrors-with-statement-mirror-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Create a regal bathroom by choosing a statement mirror for the same<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Vertical Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Horizontal mirrors are great in their own way but vertical mirrors grant a sense of dynamism to your bathroom. Moreover, in a small or a medium-sized bathroom, a vertical mirror fits like a dream.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190549\/vertical-mirror-for-bathroom.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom mirror design ideas with a vertical mirror for your bathroom makes dynamism\" class=\"wp-image-10203\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190549\/vertical-mirror-for-bathroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190549\/vertical-mirror-for-bathroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190549\/vertical-mirror-for-bathroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190549\/vertical-mirror-for-bathroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Get a vertical mirror for your bathroom to grant it some dynamism<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Avante Garde Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking for some absolutely original <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bathroom-design\/\">design for your bathroom<\/a> then an Avante Garde mirror will rise above your expectations. Sleek and custom made, this bathroom mirror design actually makes you fall in love with its originality and details.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184146\/avante-garde-mirror-for-bathroom.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom mirrors with an avante garde mirror transforms a simple bathroom into a piece of art\" class=\"wp-image-10188\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184146\/avante-garde-mirror-for-bathroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184146\/avante-garde-mirror-for-bathroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184146\/avante-garde-mirror-for-bathroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08184146\/avante-garde-mirror-for-bathroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">An Avante Garde mirror instantly transforms a simple bathroom into a piece of art<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Mirror With Lights<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Functionally, a light mirror is unbeatable. Great to be used both during nights and days, this mirror design makes your bathroom look modern and up to the minute. Neither too vain, nor too over the top, a light mirror is just perfect for any bathroom size.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190808\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-lights-1.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom mirror design with a light mirror makes your bathroom modern style\" class=\"wp-image-10204\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190808\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-lights-1.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190808\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-lights-1-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190808\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-lights-1-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190808\/bathroom-mirror-design-with-lights-1-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Light mirror can make your bathroom modern in minutes<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Minimalistic Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to bathrooms, minimalism always works. Interplay its basic function with a neat, minimalistic, framed mirror and your bathroom will stand out without a doubt!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190917\/bathroom-with-minimalistic-mirror.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom mirror design with a minimalistic mirror for streamlined bathrooms\" class=\"wp-image-10205\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190917\/bathroom-with-minimalistic-mirror.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190917\/bathroom-with-minimalistic-mirror-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190917\/bathroom-with-minimalistic-mirror-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08190917\/bathroom-with-minimalistic-mirror-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Like streamlined bathrooms? Choose this minimalistic mirror for it then<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Vanity Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your bathroom is nothing less than your personal kingdom and that\u2019s why a vanity mirror appears to be nothing but reasonable. Lit beautifully on all the sides, the vanity mirror adds that much-needed sheen to an otherwise common bathroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08191032\/bathroom-mirror-ideas-with-vanity-mirror.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom mirror ideas with a vanity mirror to create chic look\" class=\"wp-image-10206\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08191032\/bathroom-mirror-ideas-with-vanity-mirror.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08191032\/bathroom-mirror-ideas-with-vanity-mirror-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08191032\/bathroom-mirror-ideas-with-vanity-mirror-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08191032\/bathroom-mirror-ideas-with-vanity-mirror-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Bring a vanity mirror for your bathroom and create a chic space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Classic Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Last but not the least, the beauty of a simple, classic mirror is always underrated! Go for a simple framed mirror and it will make your bathroom more elegant than you ever thought it can be.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08191145\/classic-bathroom-mirror.jpg\" alt=\"Classic bathroom mirror design gives elegance look to your bathroom\" class=\"wp-image-10207\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08191145\/classic-bathroom-mirror.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08191145\/classic-bathroom-mirror-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08191145\/classic-bathroom-mirror-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/08191145\/classic-bathroom-mirror-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A classic bathroom mirror has elegance written all over it<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With so many mirrors that you can choose for your bathroom wall, we are sure, you have already picked the one! So, let it do the talking and for that extra he